headline: Countdown to Rollins (ROL) Q4 Earnings: A Look at Estimates Beyond Revenue and EPS
summary: Evaluate the expected performance of Rollins (ROL) for the quarter ended December 2025, looking beyond the conventional Wall Street top-and-bottom-line estimates and examining some of its key metrics for better insight.
